#Topology
#         PPPox Client                      DHCP/PPPoX Server                     IPv6Host
#                [STC  2/1]-------------[g0/3 DUT g5/0]------------------[STC 2/2 ]
#                 unknown             bbbb:1::1       aaaa:1::1                    aaaa:1::2
